headline: Sysco (NYSE:SYY) Reports Q3 CY2025 In Line With Expectations
summary: Food distribution giant Sysco (NYSE:SYY) met Wall Streets revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 3.2% year on year to $21.15 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.15 per share was 2.6% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
